 to its own assembly plants while 
\begin_inset Formula $d_{j,I,c}$
\end_inset

 is the proximity to its suppliers manufacturing plants.
 The summand is over the set of countries 
\begin_inset Formula $C_{j}$
\end_inset

 that firm 
\begin_inset Formula $j$
\end_inset

