\end_inset

, negative incentive to do R&D - just reduce prices.
 Where 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lambda_{f}=\frac{\left(\mu\bar{c}_{f,j}I_{f}^{-\rho}\right)^{-\theta}}{\left(\mu\bar{c}_{f,j}I_{f}^{-\rho}\right)^{-\theta}+\left(p_{\text{\text{Foreign}}}\right)^{-\theta}}
\]

\end_inset

so fixed point.
 Suppose 
